                        </note>
                        
                    
                        <note n="2" xml:id="note-t-2">
                            

<p>On 31 January 1890 <rs xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" type="person" ref="bio.xml#_416">Jo</rs> gave birth to a son, who was named <rs xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" type="person" ref="bio.xml#_418">Vincent Willem</rs>, after his godfather.</p>
                        </note>
                        
                            

                        
                    
